title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map.
description: Description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting the data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should result in the actual export of the data.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the attached report. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
